  section.section.section-what-is#what-is
    div.section__wrap.container
      h2.section__title What is Boolberry
      p.section__description BBR is a fully secure and anonymous cryptocurrency. Built from the ground up to prove anonymity, transactions cannot be linked to a sigle sender.
      div.figure-group
        figure.figure
          div.figure__icon
            img(src=require('./images/fig_blockchain.svg')).figure__img
          figcaption.figure__text
            dl
              dt.figure__strong Solving blockchain bloat
              dd.figure__regular It’s no longer necessary to drag anound hundreds of thousands of ring signatures to mantain security. Boolberry cuts blockchain length by a minimum of 50% and a maximum of 90% for faster, more efficient syncronisation.
        
        figure.figure
          div.figure__icon
            img(src=require('./images/fig_defending.svg')).figure__img
          figcaption.figure__text
            dl
              dt.figure__strong Defending against ASICs
              dd.figure__regular Boolberry employs a proprietary algoritm designed specifially to keep real miners in the game. By combating large hardware mining operations, Boolberry remains truly democratized and safe from a 51% attack.
        
        figure.figure
          div.figure__icon
            img(src=require('./images/fig_wallet.svg')).figure__img
          figcaption.figure__text
            dl
              dt.figure__strong Designing for real people
              dd.figure__regular Boolberry wallet app will finally bring an easy-to-use experience to Cryptocurrency. Building a user-friendly wallet application brings with it the possibility of widespread adoption outside the current community.
  // end section-what-is

